# This is an exemplar description of a bibliographic reference, that
applies also to all the others.
:bibliographic-reference-3 deo:BibliographicReference ;
	c4o:hasContent "3. Beck, J. (2010). Report from the Field: PubMed Central, an XML-based Archive of Life Sciences Journal Articles. In Proceedings of the International Symposium on XML for the Long Haul: Issues in the Long-term Preservation of XML. DOI: 10.4242/BalisageVol6.Beck01" .